Class MiBandObjects.HeartMonitorData

    public static class MiBandObjects.HeartMonitorData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class resembles the data structure within MiBand heart rate logs. But only the used fields are present, if others are needed they have to be added along with their respective getters.
